title: G-Shock X Complex - Rafael Pereira featuring the GA150-7A Me
description: Transit Authority - For those who know where to look, New York City is one giant playground—or skate park, or even surf paradise. Between the bankers and the goodfellas, the hipsters and the hustlers, there is a thriving community of action sports athletes. This skater Rafael Pereira knows that NYC is as raw as any place on earth for slashing, grinding, and barrel riding, and the G-Shock models they wear are just as sick, and as durable, as the city itself.

asset.author: gshockus
